survey_response.review_text: I have had experiences with many dentists before and was looking for a good dentist after moving to Mumbai in 2016. I reached out to Dr. Pal because she came highly recommended. My subsequent experience with her work supports this feedback. She help me fixed an existing crown that had come off and with a couple of dental fillings. I felt that Dr. Pal was up-to-date on recent advances in the field of dental medicine and was able to give me several alternatives - including the most economical one, which was to try to fix my existing crown rather than going for a new expensive one. I was happy that she took the time to evaluate all my options and offer me the choices.  It has been about four months since my last visit to her office and I have been satisfied with all the dental work that she did. I will definitely recommend her to anyone looking for a good dentist. It also helps that her office is conveniently located very close to the Metro Stations at Marol Naka.

Dr Shalini  Pal was able to finish off the work that my previous dentist  took months for and still left  incomplete in just 15 minutes!  She goes out of her way to ensure that the treatment is completed in good time. *** ** **** ******* *** *** **** ** ******** *** ********. I never had any instance of returning to Dr Shalini  to fix a  shoddy job. She is punctual and sticks to the appointment time. She explains the procedure well, keeps you  informed of options available and their pros and cons. She is careful while doing the procedures, very conscious about pain and tries her level best to make it comfortable for the patient. Very friendly and can put the patient at ease  ...highly recommended
